channel.title: How to make a 614 compiler
channel.description:
i did not found any 614 compiler so ill make a REALLY EASY GUIDE how to make one
make a .bat named compiler or something then just paste this code into it [code]@echo off title Compiling "C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.7.0_07\bin\javac.exe" -cp lib/cache.jar;lib/jython.jar;lib/slf4j-api-1.5.8.jar;lib/mina-core-2.0.0-M6.jar;lib/slf4j-jdk14-1.5.8.jar;lib/commons-compress-1.0.jar;lib/netty-3.1.5.GA.jar;lib/junit-4.6.jar -d bin src/dragonkk/rs2rsps/*.java src/dragonkk/rs2rsps/cache/*.java src/dragonkk/rs2rsps/events/*.java src/dragonkk/rs2rsps/io/*.java src/dragonkk/rs2rsps/model/*.java src/dragonkk/rs2rsps/model/npc/*.java src/dragonkk/rs2rsps/model/player/*.java src/dragonkk/rs2rsps/net/*.java src/dragonkk/rs2rsps/net/codec/*.java src/dragonkk/rs2rsps/rscache/*.java src/dragonkk/rs2rsps/rscache/bzip/*.java src/dragonkk/rs2rsps/scripts/*.java src/dragonkk/rs2rsps/scripts/dialogues/*.java src/dragonkk/rs2rsps/scripts/interfaces/*.java src/dragonkk/rs2rsps/scripts/items/*.java src/dragonkk/rs2rsps/scripts/objects/*.java src/dragonkk/rs2rsps/skills/combat/*.java src/dragonkk/rs2rsps/skills/construction/*.java src/dragonkk/rs2rsps/skills/woodcutting/*.java src/dragonkk/rs2rsps/skills/magic/*.java src/dragonkk/rs2rsps/skills/prayer/*.java src/dragonkk/rs2rsps/tools/*.java src/dragonkk/rs2rsps/tools/test/*.java src/dragonkk/rs2rsps/update/*.java src/dragonkk/rs2rsps/util/*.java src/dragonkk/rs2rsps/rsobjects/*.java pause[/code]
change to your jdk.
